query: 有哪些参股了渤海化学上市公司并且持股比例小于47%的股东
golden:
MATCH (s1:stock)<-[iso:is_stockholder_of]-(sh2:stockholder) WHERE s1.stock.name == '渤海化学' AND iso.shareholding_ratio < 47 RETURN sh2.stockholder.name
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)<-[h:hold]-(pof:public_offering_fund)
WHERE h.position_ratio < 47 AND s.stock.name == "化学" 
RETURN n.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)<-[h:hold]-(pof:public_offering_fund)
WHERE s.stock.name == "化学" AND h.position_ratio < 47 
RETURN n.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t2:trade)<-[bt2:belong_to]-(s:stock)<-[iso1:is_stockholder_of]-(sh1:stockholder) WHERE sh1.stockholder.name == '份服地股据' RETURN s.stock.name, t2.trade.name
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)-[bt:belong_to]->(t:trade)
WHERE s.stock.name == "份服" AND s.stock.name == "司股" 
RETURN n.name,t.trade.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[bt:belong_to]->(t:trade)
WHERE s.stock.name == "司股" AND s.stock.name == "份服" 
RETURN n.name,t.trade.name
LIMIT 50

LIMIT 50;

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND s.stock.name == "国泰君安" WITH sd.stock_data.opening_price as temp , temp
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.opening_price > temp AND s.stock.name == "国泰君安" WITH sd.stock_data.opening_price as temp , temp
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.opening_price > temp

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '航天和国防' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH td.trade_data.maximum_price AS temp MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE td.trade_data.maximum_price == temp RETURN t.trade.name
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE t.trade.name == "航天" AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN t.trade.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND t.trade.name == "航天" 
RETURN t.trade.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '金融服务' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH td.trade_data.opening_price AS temp MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE td.trade_data.opening_price >= temp RETURN t.trade.name
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE ( t.trade.name == "金融" OR t.trade.name == "服务" ) AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN n.name,t.trade.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( t.trade.name == "金融" OR t.trade.name == "服务" ) 
RETURN n.name,t.trade.name
LIMIT 50

LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND s.stock.name == "大西洋" 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE s.stock.name == "大西洋" AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '旅游和酒店' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH td.trade_data.opening_price AS temp MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE td.trade_data.opening_price == temp RETURN t.trade.name
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE ( t.trade.name == "旅游" OR t.trade.name == "酒店" ) AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN t.trade.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( t.trade.name == "旅游" OR t.trade.name == "酒店" ) 
RETURN t.trade.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (fm1:fund_manager)-[m:manage]->(pof2:public_offering_fund) WHERE fm1.fund_manager.name == '何万俟' RETURN pof2.public_offering_fund.name
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (pof:public_offering_fund)<-[m:manage]-(fm:fund_manager)
WHERE fm.fund_manager.name == "何万俟" AND pof.public_offering_fund.name == "金管理" 
RETURN pof.public_offering_fund.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (pof:public_offering_fund)<-[m:manage]-(fm:fund_manager)
WHERE pof.public_offering_fund.name == "金管理" AND fm.fund_manager.name == "何万俟" 
RETURN pof.public_offering_fund.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (sh1:stockholder)-[iso:is_stockholder_of]->(s2:stock) WHERE sh1.stockholder.name == '数团源讯' RETURN s2.stock.name
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)
WHERE ( s.stock.name == "团源" OR s.stock.name == "讯股" ) AND s.stock.name == "数团源讯" 
RETURN s.stock.name,n.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)
WHERE s.stock.name == "数团源讯" AND ( s.stock.name == "团源" OR s.stock.name == "讯股" ) 
RETURN s.stock.name,n.name
LIMIT 50

MATCH (n:industry) WHERE n.industry.name == '食品和饮料' WITH n.industry.scale AS temp1 MATCH (n:industry) WHERE n.industry.name == '化学' WITH ABS(n.industry.scale - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (indus:industry)
WHERE ( indus.industry.name == "食品" OR indus.industry.name == "饮料" ) AND indus.industry.name == "饮料" WITH indus.industry.scale as temp1
MATCH (indus:industry)
WHERE indus.industry.name == "化学" WITH indus.industry.scale as temp2 , temp1 WITH ABS( temp1 - temp2 ) as temp 
RETURN temp
LIMIT 50

MATCH (indus:industry)
WHERE ( indus.industry.name == "食品" OR indus.industry.name == "饮料" )

LIMIT 50

MATCH (n:industry) WHERE n.industry.name == '航空公司' WITH n.industry.scale AS temp1 MATCH (n:industry) WHERE n.industry.name == '制造' WITH ABS(n.industry.scale - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (indus:industry)<-[a:associate]-(s:stock)
WHERE indus.industry.name == "航空" AND indus.industry.name == "制造" 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (indus:industry)<-[a:associate]-(s:stock)
WHERE indus.industry.name == "制造" AND indus.industry.name == "航空" 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '旅游和酒店' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH td.trade_data.range AS temp1 MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)WHERE t.trade.name == '电脑硬件' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(td.trade_data.range - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( t.trade.name == "旅游" OR t.trade.name == "酒店" ) 
RETURN t.trade
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE ( t.trade.name == "旅游" OR t.trade.name == "酒店" ) AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN t.trade
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '酒店和度假村' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH td.trade_data.minimum_price AS temp1 MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)WHERE t.trade.name == '电力' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(td.trade_data.minimum_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data) WHERE s.stock.name == '福成股份' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH sd.stock_data.minimum_price AS temp1 MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)WHERE s.stock.name == '中国化学' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(sd.stock_data.minimum_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( s.stock.name == "股份" OR s.stock.name == "中国化" ) 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE ( s.stock.name == "股份" OR s.stock.name == "中国化" ) AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '金属和矿业' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH td.trade_data.opening_price AS temp1 MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)WHERE t.trade.name == '金融技术' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(td.trade_data.opening_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE ( t.trade.name == "金属" OR t.trade.name == "矿业" ) AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN temp
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( t.trade.name == "金属" OR t.trade.name == "矿业" ) 
RETURN temp
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '电力' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH td.trade_data.maximum_price AS temp1 MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)WHERE t.trade.name == '医疗保健设施' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(td.trade_data.maximum_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;

LIMIT 50;

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data) WHERE s.stock.name == '华鑫股份' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH sd.stock_data.minimum_price AS temp1 MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)WHERE s.stock.name == '红豆股份' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(sd.stock_data.minimum_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data) WHERE s.stock.name == '广西能源' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH sd.stock_data.range AS temp1 MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)WHERE s.stock.name == '中国高科' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(sd.stock_data.range - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( s.stock.name == "能源" OR s.stock.name == "中国高科" ) 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE ( s.stock.name == "能源" OR s.stock.name == "中国高科" ) AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE t.trade.name == '化学' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH td.trade_data.closing_price AS temp1 MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)WHERE t.trade.name == '金融技术' AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(td.trade_data.closing_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (indus:industry)<-[a:associate]-(s:stock)-[bt:belong_to]->(t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE ( indus.industry.name == "化学" OR indus.industry.name == "金融" ) AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (indus:industry)<-[a:associate]-(s:stock)-[bt:belong_to]->(t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( indus.industry.name == "化学" OR indus.industry.name == "金融" ) 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data) WHERE s.stock.name == '华胜天成' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH sd.stock_data.maximum_price AS temp1 MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)WHERE s.stock.name == '闻泰科技' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(sd.stock_data.maximum_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND s.stock.name == "科技" 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE s.stock.name == "科技" AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data) WHERE s.stock.name == '深圳燃气' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH sd.stock_data.range AS temp1 MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)WHERE s.stock.name == '宁波富达' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(sd.stock_data.range - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE s.stock.name == "宁波富达" AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND s.stock.name == "宁波富达" 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data) WHERE s.stock.name == '首商股份' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH sd.stock_data.opening_price AS temp1 MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)WHERE s.stock.name == '外高桥' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(sd.stock_data.opening_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE ( s.stock.name == "股份" OR s.stock.name == "外高桥" ) AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN temp
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( s.stock.name == "股份" OR s.stock.name == "外高桥" ) 
RETURN temp
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data) WHERE s.stock.name == '飞乐音响' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH sd.stock_data.opening_price AS temp1 MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)WHERE s.stock.name == '海立股份' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(sd.stock_data.opening_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( s.stock.name == "飞乐音响" OR s.stock.name == "海立股份" ) 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE ( s.stock.name == "飞乐音响" OR s.stock.name == "海立股份" ) AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data) WHERE s.stock.name == '风神股份' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH sd.stock_data.maximum_price AS temp1 MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)WHERE s.stock.name == '航天机电' AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') WITH ABS(sd.stock_data.maximum_price - temp1) as abs_diff RETURN abs_diff
LIMIT 50;
candidates:
MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE ( s.stock.name == "股份" OR s.stock.name == "航天机电" ) AND sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (s:stock)-[hsd:has_stock_data]->(sd:stock_data)
WHERE sd.stock_data.`date` == date('2023-11-11') AND ( s.stock.name == "股份" OR s.stock.name == "航天机电" ) 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50
